---

<Layout pageTitle="About" pageSiteTitles="">
	<section>
		<div class="container top-of-page">
			<div id="intro" class="spacing-btm">
				<p class="width">The following compressed timeline begins with a carousel of brochure websites, which was my introduction to HTML, CSS, and jQuery.</p>
				<p class="width">Prior to that, I worked in video production and post-production during my university years.</p>
				<p class="width">And lastly, a gallery of drawings and paintings inspired by my kids interest in markers and pencils... on the cusp of the cell phone age.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="flex padding-x align-middle borders">
				<div class="cell small-18 medium-9 small-order-2 medium-order-1">
					<div class="swiper elink">
						<div class="swiper-wrapper" id="mining">
							<div class="swiper-slide"><Picture src={anv} formats={['avif', 'webp']} alt="Allied Nevada" /></div>
							<div class="swiper-slide"><Picture src={loki} formats={['avif', 'webp']} alt="Loki Innovations" /></div>
							<div class="swiper-slide"><Picture src={terraplus} formats={['avif', 'webp']} alt="Terraplus" /></div>
							<div class="swiper-slide"><Picture src={thundermin} formats={['avif', 'webp']} alt="Thundermin" /></div>
							<div class="swiper-slide"><Picture src={rockcliff} formats={['avif', 'webp']} alt="Rockcliff" /></div>
							<div class="swiper-slide"><Picture src={queenston} formats={['avif', 'webp']} alt="Queenston Engineering" /></div>
							<div class="swiper-slide"><Picture src={riva} formats={['avif', 'webp']} alt="Riva Modeling" /></div>
							<div class="swiper-slide"><Picture src={pdac} formats={['avif', 'webp']} alt="PDAC" /></div>
							<div class="swiper-slide"><Picture src={harp} formats={['avif', 'webp']} alt="Harp Capital" /></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="cell small-18 medium-9 small-order-1 medium-order-2">
					<h1>Tabled Days</h1>
					<p>
						This carousel of dated beauties marks the beginning of a somewhat unexpected career in frontend web development, starting as a web designer. Apart from enjoying the work, the immediacy of
						creating something that could be seen by the world almost instantly was impressive.
					</p>
					<p>
						These sites were built with Microsoft FrontPage during my time with Exploration Link Ltd., a boutique web design company that provided web related services to companies in the Mining and
						Exploration Industry.
					</p>
					<p>
						<a target="_blank" class="underline" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/doug-webster-7a82a12/">Doug Webster</a>, a Geogologist and musician, started the company in the late 90's to meet the
						growing demand for an online presence for companies in the investor relations industry. I was responsible for designing and building tabled websites, posting news releases, video and image
						editing, Adobe Flash animations, and branding for print and trade show booths.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

