					<p>
						It started with drawing their oversized "Littlist Petshop" anime figurines and a plush bunny rabbit hung on the clothesline and developed into a series of b+w cartoon'ish illustrations.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="cell small-18 medium-9">
					<div class="swiper examples">
						<div class="swiper-wrapper">
							<div class="swiper-slide"><Picture src={bunny} formats={['avif', 'webp']} alt="Bunny" /><p>Bunny</p></div>
